# [ ] Switch to production API keys (remove test_ prefixes)
# [ ] Configure proper CORS_ORIGINS for your domain
# [ ] Set up SSL certificates
# [ ] Configure monitoring with Sentry
# [ ] Set up backup strategies for database and files